```plantuml
@startuml aws-solutions_automated-security-response-on-aws

actor Admin
participant "AWS Security Hub" as SecurityHub
participant "EventBridge" as EventBridge
participant "Orchestrator (Step Function)" as Orchestrator
participant "SSM Automation" as SSMAutomation
participant "AWS Lambda" as Lambda
participant "AWS Services" as AWSServices
participant "CloudWatch" as CloudWatch
participant "External Ticketing System" as TicketingSystem

Admin -> SecurityHub : Identify Security Finding
SecurityHub -> EventBridge : Trigger Custom Action
EventBridge -> Orchestrator : Start Remediation Workflow
Orchestrator -> Lambda : Parse Security Finding
Lambda -> Orchestrator : Return Parsed Data

alt Appropriate Remediation
    Orchestrator -> SSMAutomation : Execute SSM Document
else No Remediation
    Orchestrator -> Admin : Notify via CloudWatch
end

SSMAutomation -> Lambda : Execute Remediation Logic
Lambda -> AWSServices : Interact with AWS Resources
AWSServices -> Lambda : Return Status
Lambda -> SSMAutomation : Update Remediation Status

SSMAutomation -> CloudWatch : Log Remediation Outcome
SSMAutomation -> SecurityHub : Update Finding Status

alt Ticketing Enabled
    SSMAutomation -> TicketingSystem : Create Remediation Ticket
end

CloudWatch -> Admin : Alert on Failure or Success

@enduml
```